{"tid":1883120,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［青衣半導體公司］創意方法防武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-02-16T17:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T12:35:11.000Z","uid":233019,"like":100,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"d5090ae773b775e953a0f761afa15aa85c2b0514","tid":1883120,"uid":233019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:11:40.000Z","msg":"繼新年要求員工放假團年之後，<br />\n呢間&rdquo;高科技&rdquo;, &ldquo;有創意&rdquo;公司， 諗出新方法應對武漢肺炎<br />\n係人都知， 青衣周圍都有幾單確診肺炎。<br />\n佢地為左有效運用人力資源， 推出新方法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身間公司有幾層， 每層有三個區域， <br />\n新方法就係<br />\n將每一team 人分別兩組， 同時間將佢地分去唔同區域（掉位坐）。 唔俾去人地區域同其他樓層。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽聞個世紀大發現， 係有人發現個冷氣係跟唔同區咁分開。<br />\n萬一有一條友中招， 咁就只係果一個區域既人唔駛返工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗： 諗呢樣野果個， 講到出黎呢下先犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個真係天才idea.<br />\n同時間， 大家有機會坐一架廠車, 用同一個canteen。<br />\n<br />\n咁姐係有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間公司， 有成幾百人， 唔少大陸人。<br />\n聽日就正式實施， 要搬電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好想睇佢地有人中招， 係咪真係得一區唔洗返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申： 睇前公司仆街最開心"},{"pid":"3b1c0f5b7c8f3c03709fd258f8f28e026afc5240","tid":1883120,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:14:09.000Z","msg":"AXM?"},{"pid":"b0c6f191b8dfcffbe9b9